<div class="inner" id="msg_812699">BGM:特攻野郎？&lt;嘛这本是看克鲁佐的受难嘛 <img src="/bbs/Smileys/converted/em014.GIF" alt="&#58;em014" title="&#58;em014" border="0" class="smiley"/><br><br>前言<br>天宫的乱入翻译第二回！<br>今次三个类别是相当有挑战的。一是祸津神级，此类别的特技与武器都用上了古代日本汉字，要找起来得别麻烦。另外一个方阵级…只能够说梗玩很大。<br><del>之后便是AS补丁包。虽然比较少，但今次用了很多重金属危机TRPG时使用的代替用词。</del>本篇有关AS部份暂时留空<br><br><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size">目录/Index</span></strong><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">SUPPLEMENT SECTION</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;2楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 追加要素介绍<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;3楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 祸津神介绍<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">4楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 祸津神特技</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">5楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 祸津神物品</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;6楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 方阵级介绍<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">7楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 方阵级特技</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">8楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 方阵级物品</span><br>&nbsp; &nbsp;9楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <del>AS补丁包介绍</del>(暂时留空)<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;10楼&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <del><span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">AS补丁包特技</span>与<span style="color: blue;" class="bbc_color">机甲历物品</span></del>(暂时留空)<br></div>
